comments: I detest this test. The words went by way too fast and it took me about 3/4 to even see the shapes because I was too busy reading the words. Please for the love of god, if you ever do this test again give the testers a second or two more per image. From the training part of the test I barely got to learn anything and I just got used to the alphabet. The only part where I actually learned was the testing part at the end as I used trial and error to learn what words fit the shape. I tried associating the letters with the alphabet we use now and I tried to look at the first and third sign as those were the biggest indicator of the words.
